#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid "CSV Importer Plugin"
msgstr "CSV Importer dodatak"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reasons for importing CSV Files"
msgstr "Razlozi za unos CSV datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In general, it is preferable to import OFX. However, not all institutions "
"provide data in that format. CSV (comma separated value) files are almost "
"always available, sometimes described as Excel or spreadsheet files. Also, "
"they can often be created fairly easily by capturing the data you want to "
"import, such as in a text file, and manually editing it."
msgstr ""
"U globalu, poželjno je da unosite OFX. Međutim, na pružaju sve institucije "
"podatke u tom formatu. CSV (vrijednosti razdvojene zarezom) datoteke su "
"skoro uvijek dostupne, ponekad opisane i kao Excel ili tabelarno prikazane "
"datoteke. Također, često se mogu napraviti veoma lahko obilježavanjem "
"podataka koje želite unijeti, kao u tekst datoteci, i ručno ih editovati."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:17
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The primary focus of the plugin is on importing data from bank "
#| "statements, but there is also a capability to import some investment "
#| "statements. This plugin was initially created, before becoming a CSV "
#| "importer, to produce QIF files from CSV, which could then be imported. "
#| "This functionality is still present, but is likely to be removed, as the "
#| "plugin now focuses on directly importing CSV files. Also, &kappname; has "
#| "the native ability to <link linkend=\"details.impexp.qifexp\">export QIF "
#| "files</link>, so there is no real reason to produce a QIF file from a CSV "
#| "file."
msgid ""
"The initial focus of the CSV Importer was on handling data from bank "
"statements, but the ability to also import some investment statements was "
"added. In addition, it has been further enhanced to import both currency and "
"stock prices. The original code for this was initially created, before "
"becoming a CSV importer, to produce QIF files from CSV files, which could "
"then be imported. This ability is still present, but is likely to be "
"removed, as focus is now on directly importing CSV files. Also, &kmymoney; "
"has the native ability to <link linkend=\"details.impexp.qifexp\">export QIF "
"files</link>, so there is no longer a real reason to produce a QIF file from "
"a CSV file."
msgstr ""
"Primarni fokus dodatka je unos podataka bankovnih izjava, ali postoji u "
"mogućnost unosa nekih investicionih izjava. Ovaj dodatak je inicijalno "
"napravljenm prije nego što je postao CSV importer, da pravi QIF datotek iz "
"CSV, koje bi onda mogle biti unesene. Ova funkcionalnost je idalje prisutna, "
"ali će se vjerovatno ukloniti, pošto se sada dodatak fokusira na direktan "
"unos CSV datoteka. Također, &kappname; ima urođenu sposobnost da <link "
"linkend=\"details.impexp.qifexp\">eksportuje QIF datoteke</link>, pa  uopšte "
"nema razloga za pretvaranjem iz QIF u CSV datoteku."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting the plugin"
msgstr "Kako doći do dodatka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:31
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; will import CSV files. This functionality is provided as a "
#| "plugin, and it is now built into the core program, both in distro "
#| "packages and in the source files. Once the distro package is installed, "
#| "or the source files are compiled and installed, the menu choice to import "
#| "CSV files will automatically show up under the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Import</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu."
msgid ""
"The CSV importer is one of the newer features to have been added to "
"&kmymoney; in the form of a plugin. However, as with other plugins, the CSV "
"Importer is included with the core &kmymoney; source code, so it should be "
"available in all &Linux; distribution versions, as well as the versions for "
"other platforms made available through the &kmymoney; web site. The menu "
"choice to import CSV files should automatically show up under the "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> submenu."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; će unijeti CSV datoteke. Ova funkcionalnost je pružena kao "
"dodatak, i sada je ugrađena u jezgro programa, i u distro pakete i u izvorne "
"datoteke. Nakon što su distro paketi instalirani ili kada si izvorne "
"datoteke kompajlirane i instalirane, meni opcija za unos CSV datoteka će se "
"automatski prikazati u <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Import</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:41
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The CSV importer plugin is much newer than the OFX plugin, but most "
#| "distributions are now built with the CSV importer already included or "
#| "available as a separate package. Ensure that it is enabled within "
#| "&kappname;. Check the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure KMyMoney</"
#| "guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Plugins</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu. If the "
#| "CSV importer does not seem to be installed in your version, the first "
#| "place to check is in the same place you got your base &kappname; package. "
#| "See if a later version is available, or if the importer is available as a "
#| "separate package."
msgid ""
"To ensure that it is enabled within &kmymoney;, check the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item, select <guilabel>Plugins</guilabel> on "
"the left pane, and look for the <guilabel>CSV Importer</guilabel> in the "
"displayed list of plugins. If the CSV importer does not seem to be installed "
"in your version, the first place to check is in the same place you got your "
"base &kmymoney; package. See if a later version is available, or if the "
"importer is available as a separate package."
msgstr ""
"CSV importer dodatak je mnogo noviji nego OFX dodatak, ali većina "
"distribucija sada ima ugrađen CSV importer ili omogućen u vidu odvojenog "
"paketa. Osigurajte da je omogućen unutar &kappname;. Provjerite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriši KMyMoney</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Dodaci</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meni. Ukoliko CSV "
"importer nije instaliran u vašoj verziji, prvo mjesto na kojem ga trebate "
"tražiti je isto ono gdje ste nabavili svoj bazni &kappname; paket. "
"Provjerite da li je novija verzija dostupna ili da li je importet dostupan u "
"zasebnom paketu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have built from source, there should be no additional requirements. "
"The &kmymoney; build process should detect the plugin source and compile the "
"plugin. There are configuration settings which can be used to exclude this "
"or other plugins from being built, but these should rarely be needed."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing a CSV file"
msgstr "Unos CSV datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:60
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To import a CSV file, choose the importer from the menu bar: "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Import</"
#| "guimenuitem><guimenuitem>CSV...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. If CSV does "
#| "not show up under Import, you do not have the CSV Importer Plugin "
#| "installed correctly. Please see the previous section."
msgid ""
"To import a CSV file, choose the importer from the main menu: <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>CSV...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. If CSV does not show up under Import, the CSV "
"Importer Plugin is not installed correctly or is not enabled. Please see the "
"previous section."
msgstr ""
"Da biste unijeli CSV datoteku, odaberite importer iz meni bara: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Import</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>CSV...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ukoliko se CSV "
"ne pojavi pod Import, nemate CSV importer dodatak korektno instaliran. "
"Molimo vas pogledajte prethodnu sekciju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The CSV Importer is presented in the form of a wizard, with a separate page "
"for each individual step of the process."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Start"
msgstr "CSV Import čarobnjak: Poćetak"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When launched, the CSV Importer displays the <guilabel>Start</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>File</guilabel> page. On the left is a list of the steps of the "
"import process, with the current one highlighted. The upper right area is "
"where data to be imported will be displayed; before that it shows some brief "
"instructions relevant to the current stage of the wizard. Below that is a "
"set of radiobuttons for selection of the type of data to be imported. That "
"list currently includes <guilabel>Banking</guilabel>, <guilabel>Investment</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Currency prices</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Stock prices</"
"guilabel>. Next, there is a profile selector dropdown, which is enabled if "
"once the radio button has been selected for one of the import file types."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>csv import wizard: start</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>csv import wizard: start</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:100
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Lines"
msgid "CSV Import Profiles"
msgstr "CSV Import Čarobnjak: Linije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each type of CSV file to be imported requires specification of several "
"details regarding the expected formatting of the data, as described in the "
"following sections. Not only do the details differ for the different types "
"of data files imported, it is possible to need different configurations for "
"the same type of data from different sources. So you do not need to enter "
"all those details each time you import a file, the CSV Importer allows you "
"to specify the details once, and save them in a named profile."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of a CSV import profile is completely arbitrary, but will be easier "
"to remember if it reflects both the type of data being imported (bank, "
"credit card, investment, ...) and the source of the data. There is no need "
"to reference the account into which the data is imported, and it is possible "
"to use the same profile for importing into more than one account, such as "
"two checking accounts at the same bank."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The profile selector dropdown includes the names of all CSV Importer "
"profiles you have previously created, and it also lets you type the name of "
"a new profile. Below the profile selector dropdown, there are three buttons. "
"When you click <guilabel>Add</guilabel>, which is always enabled, a new "
"profile will be created with the name entered in the dropdown. Nothing will "
"happen if that field is empty or if it displays the name of an existing "
"profile. As you proceed through the rest of the CSV import wizard, the "
"various configuration settings you enter or modify will be saved in the "
"selected profile."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have previously created one or more profiles, the other two buttons "
"will be enabled. If you click <guilabel>Remove</guilabel>, the profile named "
"in the dropdown will be deleted. If you click <guilabel>Rename</guilabel>, "
"then alter the name displayed in the dropdown, and click <guilabel>Rename</"
"guilabel> again, the profile will be renamed accordingly."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:139
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Also, note the <guilabel>Skip setup</guilabel> checkbox next to the "
#| "profile selector. Initially, you should not select this check-box. Once "
#| "you have set up a profile and finished the wizard, those parameters are "
#| "saved in the resource file. Next time you use that same profile, the "
#| "parameters will be loaded into the UI (User Interface). The wizard would "
#| "then plod through the following pages of parameters that you won't need "
#| "to change. So, instead, once you are happy with a profile, it may be "
#| "helpful to check this box. The wizard will then move directly to the "
#| "final page, and, assuming no problems are found, you just have to click "
#| "<guilabel>Import</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"Next to the profile selector, there is a <guilabel>Skip setup</guilabel> "
"checkbox. Initially, you should not select this checkbox. Once you have set "
"up a profile and finished the wizard, all the configuration parameters you "
"entered are saved in the resource file under the profile name. The next time "
"you use that same profile, the parameters will be loaded into the UI (User "
"Interface). The wizard would then plod through the following pages of "
"parameters that you won't need to change. So, once you are happy with a "
"profile, it may be helpful to check this box. The wizard will then move "
"directly to the final page, and, assuming no problems are found, you just "
"have to click <guilabel>Import</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Također imajte na umu da postoji i <guilabel>Preskoči postavku</guilabel> "
"checkbox pored selektora profila. Inicijalno, ne biste trebali selektovati "
"ovaj checkbox. Nakon što ste napravili prfil i završili sa čarobnjakom, ti "
"parametri su sačuvani u resursnu datoteku. Sljedeći put kada budete "
"koristili ovaj profil, parametri će biti učitani u UI (korisnički "
"interfejs). Čarobnjak će onda proći kroz sljedeće stranice parametara koje "
"vi ne morate promijeniti. Zbog toga, kada ste zadovoljni svojim profilom, "
"možda će vam selektovanje ovog checkboxa viti korisno. Čarobnjak će onda "
"preći na završnu stranicu direktno i pod pretpostavkom da nije bilo nikakvih "
"problema, samo morate kliknuti na <guilabel>Uvoz</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom there is a <guilabel>Select File</guilabel> button. Clicking "
"this will bring up a file selector dialog to let you choose the file to "
"import. At the bottom of the remaining pages of the wizard are buttons to go "
"<guibutton>&lt; Back</guibutton> to the previous step of the wizard, move on "
"to the <guilabel>Next &gt;</guilabel> step, or <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> "
"the import."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:159
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "First select either <guilabel>Banking</guilabel> or <guilabel>Investment</"
#| "guilabel>, then click in the selector box, which displays \"Add New "
#| "Profile.\" If you have previously created any profiles, you can select "
#| "one of them, otherwise enter a new profile name, possibly the name of the "
#| "account into which you wish to import. If you enter a new profile name, "
#| "hit &Enter; to create it. Then, click on <guilabel>Select File</"
#| "guilabel>, and a standard file selector box will open, from which you "
#| "should select the CSV file you wish to import."
msgid ""
"To review, on the Start page of the wizard, first select the checkbox for "
"the type of data you are importing. In the profile selector dropdown, you "
"can select the name of a previously created CSV Importer profile, or enter a "
"new name, possibly the name of the account into which you wish to import, "
"and click <guilabel>Add</guilabel>. Finally, click <guilabel>Select File</"
"guilabel>, and a file selector dialog will open, where you select the CSV "
"file you wish to import."
msgstr ""
"Prvo odaberite ili <guilabel>Bankarstvo</guilabel> ili "
"<guilabel>Investicije</guilabel>, zatim kliknite na selektor prostor koji "
"prikazuje \"Dodaj novi profile\". Ukoliko ste prije napravili bilo kakav "
"profil, možete odabrati jedan od njih, u suprotnom unesite novo ime profila, "
"po mogućnosti ime računa u koji želite da unesete profil. Ukoliko unesete "
"ime profila, pritisnite &Enter; da biste ga napravili. Zatim kliknite na "
"<guilabel>Izaberi datotekue</guilabel> i standardni selektor datoteka će "
"biti otvoren, iz kojeg možete izabrati CSV datoteku koju želite unijeti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Separators"
msgstr "CSV Import Čarobnjak: Razdvajači"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:170
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The wizard will now have advanced to the <guilabel>Separators</guilabel> "
#| "page, and you should now see your data."
msgid ""
"After opening your selected data file, the wizard will advance to the "
"<guilabel>Separators</guilabel> page, and you should now see your data."
msgstr ""
"Čarobnjak će sada nastaviti dalje sa <guilabel>Separators</guilabel> "
"stranicom i sada biste trebali vidjeti svoje podatke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>csv import wizard: separators</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:182
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Separators"
msgid "<phrase>csv import wizard: separators</phrase>"
msgstr "CSV Import Čarobnjak: Razdvajači"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:188
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "It may appear that the displayed entries in the upper section of the "
#| "plugin window may be edited, and in fact they may, but any edits are not "
#| "kept. The table is purely for display, not for editing. The input file is "
#| "never altered by the plugin, and the data actually imported comes from "
#| "the input file, not from the display. The one exception to this is "
#| "covered in <link linkend=\"details.impexp.csv.secsym\">Securities and "
#| "Symbols</link> below."
msgid ""
"It may appear that the data displayed in the upper section of the plugin "
"window may be edited, and in fact they may, but any edits are not kept. The "
"table is purely for display, not for editing. The input file is never "
"altered by the CSV Importer, and the data actually imported comes from the "
"input file, not from the display. The one exception to this is covered in "
"<link linkend=\"details.impexp.csv.secsym\">Securities and Symbols</link> "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Možda će izgledati kao da prikazani unosi u gornjoj sekciji prozora dodatka "
"mogu biti editovane, što je i ustvari moguće, ali nikakve promjene neće biti "
"sačuvane. Tabela je tu čisto radi prikaza, ne radi editovanja.Datoteka unosa "
"nikada neće biti promijenjena od strane dodatka, i podaci koji se unose "
"dolaze iz datoteke unosa, a ne sa već pomenutog prikaza. Jedini izuzetak "
"ovome je pokriven u <link linkend=\"details.impexp.csv.secsym\">Securities "
"and Symbols</link> ispod."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The CSV Importer should have detected the appropriate <guilabel>Encoding</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Field Delimiter</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Text "
"Delimiter</guilabel>. You can change the encoding if the program did not "
"choose correctly. If you need to change the Field Delimiter, such as if your "
"data is actually tab delimited, and not a comma delimited, be aware that "
"doing so will reset any field choices you may already have made. Generally "
"the quote (&quot;) is the correct text delimiter, but you may change it as "
"necessary. Click <guibutton>Next</guibutton> to proceed."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:210
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Lines"
msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Rows"
msgstr "CSV Import Čarobnjak: Linije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will now be on the <guilabel>Rows</guilabel> or <guilabel>Lines</"
"guilabel> page. Here, you indicate if any lines should be ignored at the "
"beginning or end of the file."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>csv import wizard: rows</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>csv import wizard: rows</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page allows you to adjust the import to ignore header and footer rows "
"at the beginning or end of the file, which do not actually contain data to "
"be imported."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start line"
msgstr "Početna linija"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:235
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Set this so the importer skips any header lines in the file. Your choice "
#| "will be saved in this profile for future use. The start and end lines "
#| "interact, and the start line may not be higher than the end line. If the "
#| "<guilabel>Start line</guilabel> selector does not respond, check the end "
#| "line setting."
msgid ""
"Set this so the importer skips any header lines in the file. Your choice "
"will be saved in this profile for future use. The start and end lines "
"interact, and the start line may not be higher than the end line, nor may it "
"be higher then the actual number of lines in the file. If the "
"<guilabel>Start line</guilabel> selector does not respond, check the end "
"line setting."
msgstr ""
"Ovo postavite tako da importer preskače bilo koje header linije u vašoj "
"datoteci. Vaš izbor će biti sačuvan u ovom profilu za buduću upotrebu. "
"Poćetne i zadnje linije međusobno dejstvuju i početna linija možda neće biti "
"viša od zadnje linije. Ukoliko <guilabel>Start line</guilabel> selektor ne "
"reaguje, provjerite opcije zadnje linije."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "End line"
msgstr "Zadnja linija"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The importer will automatically set this to the last line in the file, or to "
"the setting last saved. You will only need to adjust it if there are footer "
"lines in the file the importer should ignore. Otherwise, you are likely to "
"get a data error warning when the plugin attempts to parse incorrect data. "
"Again, if the <guilabel>End line</guilabel> selector does not respond, check "
"the <guilabel>Start line</guilabel> setting."
msgstr ""
"Importer će automatski postaviti ovu liniju da bude zadnja u datoteci ili na "
"postavke koje su zadnje spašene. Samo je morate namjestiti ukoliko postoje "
"footer linije u datoteci koje bio importer trebao ignorisati. U suprotnom, "
"vjerovatno ćete dobiti upozorenje na grešku kada dodatak pokuša da raščlani "
"netačne podatke. Opet, ukoliko <guilabel>Krajnja linija</guilabel> selektor "
"ne reaguje, provjerite <guilabel>Početna linija</guilabel> postavke."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Above these two fields is a <guilabel>Header contains account name or "
"number</guilabel> checkbox. If checked, the importer will look in the lines "
"above the start line for the name of number of the account to use for the "
"import. If not, you will be prompted for that information."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are ready, click <guilabel>Next</guilabel> to proceed to the next "
"step."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:267
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Lines"
msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Columns"
msgstr "CSV Import Čarobnjak: Linije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should now be on the <guilabel>Columns</guilabel> page. This is where "
"you tell the importer which columns in the file contain the data which maps "
"to the specific fields needed to create a meaningful record or transaction, "
"depending on the type of data being imported. There is a different version "
"of this page for each type of data, as each requires a different combination "
"of items."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Banking"
msgstr "CSV Import Čarobnjak: Bankarenje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>csv import wizard: banking</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>csv import wizard: banking</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For most fields, you just need to use the dropdown to select the appropriate "
"column. Note that many fields have an <quote>x</quote> button to the right. "
"Clicking it will clear whatever value has been entered or selected in the "
"field to the left. In addition, there are some special considerations."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:298
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the center are two radio buttons. If your file has a single column for "
#| "all values, select <guilabel>Amount col</guilabel>. However, if there are "
#| "separate columns for debits and credits, select <guilabel>Debit/credit "
#| "col</guilabel>. This will enable either the <guilabel>Amount column</"
#| "guilabel> selector or the <guilabel>Debit column</guilabel> and "
#| "<guilabel>Credit column</guilabel> selectors."
msgid ""
"To the right is an area with two tabs. If your file has a single column for "
"all values, select the <guilabel>Amount</guilabel> tab. However, if there "
"are separate columns for debits and credits, select the <guilabel>Debit/"
"credit</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"U centru se nalaze dva radio dugmeta. Ukoliko vaša datoteka ima samo jednu "
"kolonu za sve vrijednosti, odaberite <guilabel>Kolona iznosa</guilabel>. "
"Ipak, ukoliko postoje odvojene kolone za dugove i kredite, odaberite "
"<guilabel>Dugovna/potražna kolona</guilabel>. Ovo će omogućiti ili "
"<guilabel>Kolona iznosa</guilabel> selektor ili <guilabel>Dugovnu kolonu</"
"guilabel> i <guilabel>Potražnu kolonu</guilabel> selektore."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the Amount tab, start by selecting the column which contains the amount "
"of the transaction. If there is a column which contains <quote>Credit</"
"quote> or <quote>Debit</quote> to indicate which the amount is, select that "
"column as the <guilabel>Debit/Credit Indicator</guilabel>. Separately, if "
"there is a string included in the amount field which indicates the amount is "
"either a credit or a debit, enter that string in the appropriate "
"<guilabel>Indicator</guilabel> field. Finally, if despite setting all the "
"above values correctly, the amount imported is reversed from what it should "
"be, check the <guilabel>Opposite signs</guilabel> checkbox."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the Debit/credit tab, simply enter the numbers of the columns with those "
"values in the appropriate fields."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:324
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "It is possible to select more than one column for the Memo field, by "
#| "consecutive selections. Memo columns already selected are marked in the "
#| "drop-down with an asterisk (*). If you select multiple columns in this "
#| "way, their contents will be concatenated in the Memo field."
msgid ""
"It is possible to select more than one column for the Memo field, by making "
"consecutive selections. Memo columns already selected are indicated in the "
"<guilabel>Memo columns:</guilabel> field. If you select multiple columns in "
"this way, their contents will be concatenated in the Memo field."
msgstr ""
"Moguće je odabrati više od jedne kolone za Memo polje, uzastopnim odabirima. "
"Memo kolone su već selektirane i označene u opadajućoj listi sa zvjezdicom "
"(*). Ukoliko odaberete više kolona na ovaj način, njihov sadržaj če biti "
"postavljen i u Memo polje."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:333
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you attempt to choose the same column number for two fields, the "
#| "plugin will alert you and clear both selections. However, it is possible, "
#| "if desired, to use the same column in both the <guilabel>Payee/"
#| "Description</guilabel> and <guilabel>Memo</guilabel> fields. If you "
#| "select a column for the <guilabel>Payee/Description</guilabel> field, and "
#| "then select the same field for the <guilabel>Memo</guilabel> field, you "
#| "will receive a warning that duplicate columns have been selected, but "
#| "asking if you wish to proceed. If you do, click <guibutton>Yes</"
#| "guibutton>."
msgid ""
"If you attempt to choose the same column number for two fields, the importer "
"will alert you and clear both selections. However, it is possible, if "
"desired, to use the same column in both the <guilabel>Payee/Description</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Memo</guilabel> fields. If you select a column for "
"the <guilabel>Payee/Description</guilabel> field, and then select the same "
"column for the <guilabel>Memo</guilabel> field, you will receive a warning "
"that duplicate columns have been selected, but asking if you wish to "
"proceed. If you do, click <guibutton>Yes</guibutton>, and the column will be "
"used for both fields."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko pokušate da odaberete istu kolonu za dva polja, dodatak će vas "
"upozoriti i očistiti obje selekcije. Ipak, moguće je, ukoliko želite, "
"iskoristiti istu kolonu za oba <guilabel>Primalac/Opis</guilabel> i "
"<guilabel>Memo</guilabel> polja. Ukoliko odaberete kolonu za "
"<guilabel>Primalac/Opis</guilabel> polje, onda odaberite isto polje za "
"<guilabel>Memo</guilabel> polje, bićete upozoreni da su duple kolone "
"odabrane, ali će vas upitati da li želite nastaviti. Ukoliko želite, "
"kliknite na <guibutton>Da</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:346
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "One particular reason to also capture the Payee/Descriptor field in the "
#| "Memo field is that the incoming Payee/Description field might get "
#| "completely changed on import when &kappname; does transaction matching. "
#| "Selecting that field also as Memo will preserve that data, which would "
#| "otherwise get lost."
msgid ""
"One particular reason to also capture the Payee/Descriptor field in the Memo "
"field is that the incoming Payee/Description field might get completely "
"changed on import when &kmymoney; does transaction matching. Selecting that "
"field also as Memo will preserve that data, which would otherwise get lost."
msgstr ""
"Jedan određen razlog da biste obilježili Primalac/Opis polje u Memo polju je "
"da dolazeće Primalac/Opis polje može u potpunosti biti promijenjeno prilikom "
"unosa kada &kappname; uradi povezivanje transakcija. Odabir tog polja kao i "
"Memo polja će sačuvati podatke, koji bi u suprotnom bili izgubljeni."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:355
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you notice you have made an incorrect choice, just change that "
#| "selection. If several changes need to be made, click the <guilabel>Clear</"
#| "guilabel> button."
msgid ""
"If you notice you have made an incorrect choice, just change that selection. "
"If several changes need to be made, you can click <guilabel>Clear all</"
"guilabel> and start over."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko primijetite da ste napravili pogrešan izbor, samo promijenite "
"odabir. Ukoliko morate napraviti više izmjena, kliknite <guilabel>Očisti</"
"guilabel> dugme."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once columns have been chosen for all the necessary fields, the "
"<guilabel>Next</guilabel> button will be enabled, and clicking it will "
"advance the wizard."
msgstr ""
"Kada su kolone odabrane za sva potrebna polja, <guilabel>Sljedeći</guilabel> "
"dugme će biti omogućeno, i klikom na njega će čarobnjak nastaviti dalje."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:368
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Start"
msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Format"
msgstr "CSV Import čarobnjak: Poćetak"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next page of the wizard still shows the data to be imported on the top, "
"but the lower section provides three dropdowns. The initial values are set "
"by &kmymoney; based on examining the actual data."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:376 details-impexp-csv.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>csv import wizard: investment</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:382 details-impexp-csv.docbook:431
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Investment"
msgid "<phrase>csv import wizard: investment</phrase>"
msgstr "CSV Import Čarobnjak: Investicije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Decimal Symbol</guilabel> defaults to <quote>auto,</quote> "
"which usually produces the correct results. If not, you can explicitly "
"specify the <quote>dot</quote> or <quote>comma.</quote>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Thousands Symbol</guilabel> is set automatically, and the "
"field may be disabled if it will not affect the results."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:398
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This needs to be set according to the order of year, month, and day in "
#| "the dates in the file. If the plugin finds data incompatible with this "
#| "setting, it will complain when you try to import. However, if the setting "
#| "is wrong, but does not produce invalid results (such as data with no days "
#| "higher than 12, so month and day could be switched) you will simply get "
#| "incorrect data, because the plugin cannot know you made a mistake. In "
#| "this case, the error will be obvious in the ledger after import."
msgid ""
"This needs to be set according to the order of year, month, and day in the "
"dates in the file. If the plugin finds data incompatible with this setting, "
"it will complain when you try to import. However, if the setting is wrong, "
"but it produce invalid results not detected (such as data with no days "
"higher than 12, so month and day could be switched) you will simply get "
"incorrect data, because the plugin cannot know you made a mistake. In this "
"case, the error will be obvious in the ledger after import."
msgstr ""
"Ovo mora biti postavljeno u skladu sa redoslijedom godine, mjeseca i dana u "
"datumima u vašoj datoteci. Ukoliko dodatak primijeti da su podaci "
"neuskladivi, žaliće se prilikom pokušaja unosa. Ipak, ukoliko su postavke "
"pogrešne, ali ne daju pogrešan rezultat (podaci sa datumima u kojima se ne "
"nalaze dani veći od broja 12, pa prilikom zamjene dana i mjeseci ne dolazi "
"do problema) samo ćete dobiti pogrešne podatke, zato što dodatak ne može "
"znati da li ste vi napravili grešku. U tom slučaju, greška će biti očigledna "
"u glavnom pregledniku nakon unosa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Date format</guilabel> specifies the order of day, month, and "
"year, and is also set automatically. However, in some cases, such as data "
"with no day higher than 12, you will notice the problem after the import. In "
"such cases, you will need to repeat the import, and choose the actual order "
"of the date components."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Investment"
msgstr "CSV Import Čarobnjak: Investicije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page is similar to the <guilabel>Banking</guilabel> page, although it "
"is somewhat more complex. Most selections are fairly obvious, but there are "
"some items which can seem confusing until you have completed the process "
"once or twice."
msgstr ""
"Ova stranica je slična <guilabel>Bankarstvo</guilabel> stranici, iako je "
"malo kompleksnija. Većina selekcija je veoma očita, ali postoje neke stvari "
"koje mogu izgledati zbunjujuće sve dok ne završite proces jednom ili dva "
"puta."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As on the <guilabel>Banking</guilabel> page, you may select more than one "
"column for the Memo field"
msgstr ""
"Kao i na <guilabel>Bankarstvo</guilabel> stranici, možete odabrati više od "
"jedne kolone za Memo polje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:446
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Type/Action</guilabel> selector is to identify the column "
#| "which contains the action type, such as Buy, Sell, Dividend, etc."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Type/Action</guilabel> selector is to identify the column "
"which contains the action type, such as Buy, Sell, Dividend, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Tip/Akcija</guilabel> selektor služi za identifikaciju kolona koje "
"sadrže akcijske tipove, kao što su Kupovina, Prodaja, Dividenda, itd."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:453
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Price Fraction</guilabel> selector is to indicate the "
#| "fraction/multiplier for compatibility between imported and stored prices. "
#| "For instance, if the import file price is in cents, but your &kappname; "
#| "account is priced in dollars, select 0.01. Or, if your &kappname; data "
#| "file pricing is in dollars, and so is the CSV file being imported, then "
#| "set <guilabel>Price Fraction</guilabel> to 1.0."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Price Fraction</guilabel> selector is to indicate the fraction/"
"multiplier for compatibility between imported and stored prices. For "
"instance, if the import file price is in cents, but your &kmymoney; account "
"is priced in dollars, select 0.01. Or, if your &kmymoney; data file pricing "
"is in dollars, and so is the CSV file being imported, then set "
"<guilabel>Price Fraction</guilabel> to 1.0."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dijelovi cijena</guilabel> selektor služi za indikaciju frakcije/"
"multiplikatora za kompatibilnost između unesenih i uskladištenih cijena. "
"Npr., ukoliko je cijena datoteke unosa izražena u centima, ali vaš "
"&kappname; račun je izražen u dolarima, odaberite 0.01. Ili ukoliko je "
"cijena u vašoj &kappname; datoteci izražena u dolarima kao i CSV datoteka "
"koja se unosi, onda <guilabel>Dijelovi cijena</guilabel> postavite na 1.0."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:464
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Use the <guilabel>Fee Column</guilabel> selector if your file has a "
#| "distinct column for fees. Beware, though, that the fee might have been "
#| "taken into account in the price. If there is a fee, and it is a "
#| "percentage figure, rather than a value, click the <guilabel>Fee is "
#| "percentage</guilabel> check box. Note that on this page, this is the only "
#| "field to explicitly include \"column\" in the label, to emphasize that it "
#| "is for the fee column, not for any actual fee."
msgid ""
"There are two ways to specify fees for transactions. If your file has a "
"distinct column for fees, use the <guilabel>Fee Column</guilabel> selector. "
"Note that on this page, this is the only field to explicitly include \"column"
"\" in the label, to emphasize that it is for the fee column, not for any "
"actual fee. Beware, though, that the fee might have been taken into account "
"in the price."
msgstr ""
"Koristite <guilabel>Kolona naknada</guilabel> selektor ukoliko vaša datoteka "
"ima različite kolone za naknade. Imajte na umu da naknade mogu biti "
"uračunate u cijenu. Ukoliko postoji nadoknada i u obliku je postotka, a ne "
"vrijednosti, kliknite na <guilabel>Naknada je procentualna</guilabel> "
"checkbox. Imajte na umu da na ovoj stranici, ovo je jedin polje koje "
"eksplicitno uključuje \"kolonu\" u labeli, kako bi bilo naglašeno daje za "
"kolonu nadoknada, a ne za stvarne nadoknade."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is a fee, but it is a percentage figure, rather than a specified "
"value, click the <guilabel>Fee is percentage</guilabel> check box, and enter "
"the percentage rate into the <guilabel>Fee rate</guilabel> field. In "
"addition, if there is a minimum fee, specify it in the <guilabel>Minimal "
"Fee</guilabel> field, which becomes enabled when you enter the Fee rate "
"(with a decimal point.) At this point, clicking <guibutton>Calculate Fees</"
"guibutton> will add a column at the right of the table above, and will "
"indicate the calculated fee for each transaction."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you made a mistake in entering the fee information, clicking "
"<guibutton>Clear Fee</guibutton> will reset all the fee related fields to "
"their initial values."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the column selectors are two areas for the security identity. "
"Depending upon your broker or financial institution, your file may contain "
"entries for only one or for several securities."
msgstr ""
"Ispod selektora kolona se nalaze dva područja za sigurnost identiteta. U "
"ovisnosti o vašem brokeru ili finansijskoj ustanovi, vaša datoteka može "
"sadržavati unose za samo jedan ili za više sigurnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:497
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the file contains transactions for just a single security, with the "
#| "name possibly in a header row, the name should be entered into the "
#| "<guilabel>Security Name</guilabel> box. The name you enter will be added "
#| "to the drop-down list for future use. You may subsequently wish to remove "
#| "that name from the list. If so, select it, then click the <guilabel>Hide "
#| "security</guilabel> button. This removes it only from this list, and has "
#| "no effect on your main &kappname; file."
msgid ""
"If the file contains transactions for just a single security, with the name "
"possibly in a header row, the name should be entered into the "
"<guilabel>Security Name</guilabel> box. The name you enter will be added to "
"the dropdown list for future use. You may subsequently wish to remove that "
"name from the list. If so, select it, then click <guilabel>Hide security</"
"guilabel>. This removes it only from this list, and has no effect on your "
"main &kmymoney; file."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko datoteka sadrži transakcije za samo jednu sigurnost, sa nazivom "
"možda u header redu, ime se treba unijeti u <guilabel>Security Name</"
"guilabel> polje. Ime koje unesete će biti dodano u opadajuću listu za buduće "
"upotrebe. Možda ćete zatim htjeti da uklonite ime sa liste. Ukoliko je to "
"slučaj, onda kliknite na <guilabel>Hide security</guilabel> dugme. Ovo ga "
"samo uklanja iz liste i nema nikakvog utjecaja na vašu glavnu &kappname; "
"datoteku."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:509
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the file includes transactions for several securities, each will be "
#| "identified by its ticker symbol in a column with further detail in "
#| "another column. Select those columns in the <guilabel>Symbol</guilabel> "
#| "and <guilabel>Detail</guilabel> selectors. It may be that a security has "
#| "no official symbol, and in this case a pseudo-symbol may be invented; "
#| "this is not a problem, as long as it uniquely identifies that security in "
#| "the import file. Sometimes the actual activity type is embedded in the "
#| "detail column, possibly prefixed by a standard text. For instance, if the "
#| "field contains <quote>type: dividend</quote>, enter into the "
#| "<guilabel>Filter text</guilabel> box <quote>type: </quote> including the "
#| "trailing space."
msgid ""
"If the file includes transactions for several securities, each will be "
"identified by its ticker symbol in a column with further detail in another "
"column. Select those columns in the <guilabel>Symbol</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Detail</guilabel> selectors. It may be that a security has no "
"official symbol, and in this case a pseudo-symbol may be invented; this is "
"not a problem, as long as it uniquely identifies that security in the import "
"file. Sometimes the actual activity type is embedded in the detail column, "
"possibly prefixed by a standard text. For instance, if the field contains "
"<quote>type: dividend</quote>, go to <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> text box "
"and enter <quote>type: </quote> including the trailing space."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko datoteka uključuje transakcije za više sigurnosti, svaka će biti "
"identifikovana pomoću svog simbola u koloni sa više detalja u drugoj koloni. "
"Odaberite te kolone u <guilabel>Symbol</guilabel> i <guilabel>Detail</"
"guilabel> selektorima. Moguće je da sigurnost nema oficijalni simbol, i u "
"ovom slučaju se izmisli pseudo-simbol; to nije problem sve dok se pomoću "
"njega jednoznačno identificira sigurnost u unosu datoteke. Ponekad je "
"stvarni tip aktivnosti ugrađen u kolonu detalja, vjerovatno sa prefiksom "
"standardnog teksta. Npr., ukoliko polje sadrži <quote>type: dividend</"
"quote>, unesite u <guilabel>Filter text</guilabel> prostor <quote>type: </"
"quote> uključujući prostor iza."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When all required fields are selected, the <guilabel>Next</guilabel> button "
"will be enabled, and clicking it will advance the wizard."
msgstr ""
"Kada su sva obavezna polja selektirana, <guilabel>Sljedeći</guilabel> dugme "
"će biti omogućeno i klikom na njega nastavljate dalje sa čarobnjakom."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "CSV Import Wizard: Securities and Symbols"
msgstr "CSV Import Čarobnjak: Sigurnosti i simboli"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:535
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For an Investment file, after the <guilabel>Lines</guilabel> page has "
#| "been accepted, you need to assure that each security in the file is "
#| "matched to the correct security in your &kappname; file, before import "
#| "can proceed. At this point, another window will open, showing the "
#| "securities and symbols contained in the import file. Note that unlike the "
#| "data display in the main wizard windows, the changes you make on this "
#| "page <emphasis>are</emphasis> imported."
msgid ""
"For an Investment file, after the <guilabel>Columns</guilabel> page has been "
"accepted, you need to assure that each security in the file is matched to "
"the correct security in your &kmymoney; file, before import can proceed. At "
"this point, another window will open, showing the securities and symbols "
"contained in the import file. Note that unlike the data display in the main "
"wizard windows, the changes you make on this page <emphasis>are</emphasis> "
"imported."
msgstr ""
"Za Investment datoteku, nakon što je <guilabel>Linije</guilabel> stranica "
"prihvaćena, morate osigurati da je svaka sigurnost u datoteci povezana sa "
"odgovarajućom sigurnosti u vašoj &kappname; datoteci prije nego što "
"nastavite sa unosom. U ovom trenutku, još jedan prozor će se otvoriti, koji "
"će pokazati sve sigurnosti i simbole sadržane u datoteci koja se unosi. "
"Imajte na umu da za razliku od podatak prikazanih u glavnom prozoru "
"čarobnjaka, promjene koje napravite na ovoj stranici<emphasis>će biti</"
"emphasis> unesne."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid "Completing this page is straightforward, if you consider these items:"
msgstr ""
"Popunjavanje ove stranice je veoma jednostavno ukoliko uzmete u obzir "
"sljedeće stvari:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each row represents one transaction, and so it may appear there are "
"duplicate rows. This is OK."
msgstr ""
"Svaki red predstavlja jednu transakciju, pa može izgledati da imate duple "
"redove. To je UREDU."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:555
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Each security name must match exactly the existing security as specified "
#| "in &kappname;. If it does not match, it will be created as a new "
#| "security, which you probably do not want, unless it represents the "
#| "purchase of a new security."
msgid ""
"Each security name must match exactly the existing security as specified in "
"&kmymoney;. If it does not match, it will be created as a new security, "
"which you probably do not want, unless it represents the purchase of a new "
"security."
msgstr ""
"Svako ime sigurnosti mora odgovarati tačno postojećoj sigurnosti "
"specificiranoj u &kappname;. Ukoliko ne odgovara, biće napravljena kao nova "
"sigurnost, što vjerovatno ne želite, osim ukoliko predstavlja kupovinu nove "
"sigurnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid "A symbol must be shown for each security."
msgstr "Simbol mora biti prikazan za svaku sgurnost."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>only</emphasis> information on this page should be the "
"security symbol and name. Any other information initially shown (such as "
"date or activity type) is still in the actual import file, but should not be "
"shown here."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Jedina</emphasis> informacija na ovoj stranici bi trebal biti "
"simbol sigurnosti i njeno ime. Bilo koja druga informacija inicijalno "
"prikazana (kao što je datum ili tip aktivnosti) je idalje u stvarnoj "
"datoteci unosa, ali ne treba biti prikazano tu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:580
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can edit a symbol or security name by double clicking the cell. For "
#| "each security, if necessary, edit the name in one of its rows, If the "
#| "correct security name appears in the imported file, double click on it to "
#| "select it, then copy and paste/edit, taking care if you have used a "
#| "variation or abbreviation within &kappname;. If you edit a security name, "
#| "that edit will be applied to all rows with the same symbol."
msgid ""
"You can edit a symbol or security name by double-clicking the cell. For each "
"security, if necessary, edit the name in one of its rows, If the correct "
"security name appears in the imported file, double-click it to select it, "
"then copy and paste/edit, taking care if you have used a variation or "
"abbreviation within &kmymoney;. If you edit a security name, that edit will "
"be applied to all rows with the same symbol."
msgstr ""
"Možete editovati simbol ili ime sigurnosti duplim klikom na ćeliju. Za svaku "
"sigurnost, ukoliko je potrebno, editujte ime u jednom od njenih redova, "
"ukoliko se ispravno ime sigurnosti pojavi u unesenoj datoteci, duplik klikom "
"ga selektirajte, zatim ga kopirajte, uzimajući u obzir da li ste koristili "
"neke varijacije ili kratice unutar &kappname;. Ukoliko promijenite ime "
"sigurnosti, ta promjena će biti primijenjena u svim redovima sa istim "
"simbolom."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:589
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Any line without a symbol will be treated as a brokerage-type checking "
#| "item. If any transaction involves another account, &eg;, a checking or "
#| "brokerage account for a received dividend or for making a payment, a "
#| "message box will pop up for the account name to be entered for the "
#| "transfer. This will generally be the Brokerage account you chose or "
#| "created when you created the Investment account. Similarly enter the "
#| "column number containing the payee, if requested. If a mistake is made "
#| "when entering the account name, the import will go ahead, but &kappname; "
#| "will not recognize it, and will flag those transactions as missing a "
#| "category assignment. If the required account name is rather long, just "
#| "enter a few characters. The import will proceed but the transactions will "
#| "be flagged by &kappname; as missing a category assignment, and you will "
#| "need to select the correct transfer account after the import. Click "
#| "<guilabel>OK</guilabel> when done. The import process then gets handed "
#| "over to &kappname;"
msgid ""
"Any line without a symbol will be treated as a brokerage-type checking item. "
"If any transaction involves another account, &eg;, a checking or brokerage "
"account for a received dividend or for making a payment, a message box will "
"pop up for the account name to be entered for the transfer. This will "
"generally be the Brokerage account you chose or created when you created the "
"Investment account. Similarly enter the column number containing the payee, "
"if requested. If a mistake is made when entering the account name, the "
"import will go ahead, but &kmymoney; will not recognize it, and will flag "
"those transactions as missing a category assignment. If the required account "
"name is rather long, just enter a few characters. The import will proceed "
"but the transactions will be flagged by &kmymoney; as missing a category "
"assignment, and you will need to select the correct transfer account after "
"the import. Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> when done. The import process "
"then gets handed over to &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Bilo koja linija bez simbola će biti tretirana kao stavka provjere "
"brokerskog tipa. Ukoliko bilo koja transakcija uključi neki drugi račun, "
"&eg;, tekući ili brokerski račun za primanje dividendi ili za vršenje "
"isplate, prozor poruke će se pojaviti kako bi se unijelo ime računa za taj "
"transfer. Ovo će generalno biti brokerski račun koji ste vi odabrali ili "
"kreirali prilikom pravljenja investicionog računa. Slično unesite broj "
"kolone koji sadrži osobu povezanu sa plaćanjem, ukoliko se zahtijeva. "
"Ukoliko dođe do greške pri unosu imena računa, unos će nastaviti dalje, ali "
"ga &kappname; neće prepoznati i označiće te transakcije kao da im nedostaje "
"dodjela kategorije. Ukoliko je ime računa veoma dugo, samo unesite nekoliko "
"znakova. Unos će biti nastavljen, ali će &kappname; obilježiti transakcije "
"kao da im nedostaje dodjela kategorije i moraćete odabrati odgovarajući "
"račun transfera nakon unosa. Kliknite <guilabel>OK</guilabel> kada ste "
"završili. Proces unosa se potom predaje u ruke &kappname;."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:606
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have more that one transaction referring to the same security, you "
#| "can edit all of them at once, using multi-select. For instance, to add a "
#| "symbol for several lines, press and hold the <keysym>CTL</keysym> key, "
#| "and in the symbol column, select each transaction. While still holding "
#| "the <keysym>CTL</keysym> key, all those symbol cells should still be "
#| "selected, so click on one and enter the symbol. Click inside the window "
#| "but outside that column, or hit <keysym>Enter</keysym> (not <guilabel>OK</"
#| "guilabel>). Now that those transactions all have the same symbol, double "
#| "click one detail entry and edit the security name as you wish. Click "
#| "elsewhere on the window (or <keysym>Enter</keysym>) to accept the edit, "
#| "which will then change all those entries. The remaining entries will show "
#| "the symbols picked up from the transactions in the import file."
msgid ""
"If you have more that one transaction referring to the same security, you "
"can edit all of them at once, using multi-select. For instance, to add a "
"symbol for several lines, press and hold the &Ctrl; key, and in the symbol "
"column, select each transaction. While still holding the &Ctrl; key, all "
"those symbol cells should still be selected, so click one and enter the "
"symbol. Click inside the window but outside that column, or hit &Enter; (not "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>). Now that those transactions all have the same "
"symbol, double-click one detail entry and edit the security name as you "
"wish. Click elsewhere on the window (or &Enter;) to accept the edit, which "
"will then change all those entries. The remaining entries will show the "
"symbols picked up from the transactions in the import file."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko imate više od jedne transakcije koja se odnosi na istu sigurnost, "
"možete ih sve editovati odjednom, pomoću opcije multi-select.Npr., da biste "
"dodali simbol za više linija, pritisnite i držite <keysym>CTL</keysym> tipku "
"i u koloni simbola odaberite svaku transakciju. Dok držite <keysym>CTL</"
"keysym> tipku i kad su sve ćelije simbola selektirane, kliknite na jednu i "
"unesite simbol. Kliknite unutar prozora ali van te kolone ili pritisnite "
"<keysym>Enter</keysym> (ne <guilabel>OK</guilabel>). Sada kada sve te "
"transakcije imaju isti simbol, duplim klikom na jedan unos detalja možete "
"editovati ime sigurnosti kako želite. Kliknite bilo gdje drugo u prozoru "
"(ili <keysym>Enter</keysym>) da biste prihvatili ovu promjenu, koje će onda "
"promijeniti sve te unose. Ostali unosi će prikazivati simbole odabrane iz "
"transakcija prilikom unosa datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:619
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Now click <guilabel>OK</guilabel>, then <guilabel>Import</guilabel>. In "
#| "the <guilabel>Enter Account</guilabel> box, enter the name of a Brokerage/"
#| "checking account for funds. If you enter a valid name that account will "
#| "be used. If you can't be bothered entering a correct but long name, enter "
#| "a few characters. The import will accept that but the transactions in the "
#| "ledger after import will need a proper account to be selected. For the "
#| "<guilabel>Brokerage Item</guilabel> box, enter the number of the column "
#| "containing that detail. Now, on the <guilabel>Invalid transaction</"
#| "guilabel> box you may get a few entries because the activity type does "
#| "not match the qty/price/amount combination. On each message, click "
#| "<guilabel>Select Transaction Type</guilabel>, and a drop down will appear "
#| "indicating valid activity types for that combination of values."
msgid ""
"Now click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, then <guibutton>Import</guibutton>. In "
"the <guilabel>Enter Account</guilabel> box, enter the name of a Brokerage/"
"checking account for funds. If you enter a valid name that account will be "
"used. If you can't be bothered entering a correct but long name, enter a few "
"characters. The import will accept that but the transactions in the ledger "
"after import will need a proper account to be selected. For the "
"<guilabel>Brokerage</guilabel> box, enter the number of the column "
"containing that detail. Now, on the <guilabel>Invalid transaction</guilabel> "
"box you may get a few entries because the activity type does not match the "
"qty/price/amount combination. On each message, click <guilabel>Select "
"Transaction Type</guilabel>, and a dropdown will appear indicating valid "
"activity types for that combination of values."
msgstr ""
"Sada kliknite na <guilabel>U redu</guilabel>, a potom na <guilabel>Uvoz</"
"guilabel>. U <guilabel>Unesi račun</guilabel>  prostoru unesite ime "
"brokerskog/tekućeg računa za sredstva. Ukoliko unesete ispravno ime, taj "
"račun će se koristiti. Ukoliko nemate živaca da unesete ispravno ali dugačko "
"ime, unesite samo nekoliko znakova. Unos će biti prihvaćen ali ćete morati "
"odabrati odgovarajući račun u glavnom pregledu. Za <guilabel>Brokerska "
"stavka</guilabel> prostor, unesite broj kolona koje sadrže detalje. Sada na "
"<guilabel>Invalid transaction</guilabel> prostori možete dobiti par unosa "
"zato što tip aktivnosti ne odgovara qty/cijena/vrijednost kombinaciji. Za "
"svaku poruku, kliknite <guilabel>Odaberi vrstu transakcije</guilabel> i "
"opadajuća lista će se pojaviti uključujući validne tipove aktivnosti za te "
"kombinacije vrijednsti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-csv.docbook:634
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Now the import has occurred and you're into KMM to select the investment "
#| "account to use. Then the checking account, if there were any brokerage "
#| "type transactions."
msgid ""
"Now the import has occurred and you're into &kmymoney; to select the "
"investment account to use. Then the checking account, if there were any "
"brokerage type transactions."
msgstr ""
"Sada je unos završen i vi se nalazite u KMM kako biste odabrali investicioni "
"račun koji ćete koristiti. Potom tekući račun, ukoliko je bilo nekih "
"transakcija brokerskog tipa."

#. Tag: title
